Note: I took over the maintainence of FIGlet for OS/2 after the release of
version 2.2.  This file should have come in a zip distribution labeled
figletos2-22a.zip  It is identical to the previous 2.2 distribution with the
following exceptions:
  * Small modifications in the REXX command files.
  * Porting of manual files to OS/2 INF format.
  * Small documentation changes to reflect the two above changes.

